*ENVIRONMENT MODIFICATIONS
! Growth chamber: constant temperature per treatment with treatment-specific RH and CO2 targets
! Daily avg temps: t1=21.25C, t2=24.75C, t3=30.75C, t4=33.75C (5C day-night differential)
! RH and CO2 ranges are assigned by temperature group and apply to both cultivars within each group:
!   BG23_21C and WG_21C: RH=37-81%, CO2=390-420 ppm
!   BG23_25C and WG_25C: RH=59-79%, CO2=620-650 ppm
!   BG23_31C and WG_31C: RH=41-68%, CO2=470-620 ppm
!   BG23_34C and WG_34C: RH=55-73%, CO2=385-602 ppm
! ECO2 below uses temperature-group midpoint CO2 values:
!   21.25C group=405 ppm, 24.75C group=635 ppm, 30.75C group=545 ppm, 33.75C group=494 ppm
! EMAX = avg + 2.5C (day), EMIN = avg - 2.5C (night)
! t1: day=23.75->24C, night=18.75->19C
! t2: day=27.25->27C, night=22.25->22C
! t3: day=33.25->33C, night=28.25->28C
! t4: day=36.25->36C, night=31.25->31C
@E ODATE EDAY  ERAD  EMAX  EMIN  ERAIN ECO2  EDEW  EWIND ENVNAME
 1 24001   -99   -99   -99   -99 A 0.0 R 405 A   0 A   0 t1_21.25C_g3_Dec2024
 2 24043   -99   -99   -99   -99 A 0.0 R 635 A   0 A   0 t2_24.75C_g6_Jan2025
 3 24085   -99   -99   -99   -99 A 0.0 R 545 A   0 A   0 t3_30.75C_g9_Apr2025
 4 24127   -99   -99   -99   -99 A 0.0 R 494 A   0 A   0 t4_33.75C_g12_May2025

