! =============================================================================
! DONALD COON TEMPERATURE x VARIETY EXPERIMENT - HYDROPONIC NFT
! =============================================================================
! Grow cycles: 3 replications per temperature treatment (g3-g5=t1, g6-g8=t2,
!              g9-g11=t3, g12-g14=t4); representative first cycle used per treatment
!
! Temperature treatments (5C day/night differential):
!   t1 = 21.25C avg  (day 23.75C / night 18.75C)  grow cycles: g3, g4, g5
!   t2 = 24.75C avg  (day 27.25C / night 22.25C)  grow cycles: g6, g7, g8
!   t3 = 30.75C avg  (day 33.25C / night 28.25C)  grow cycles: g9, g10, g11
!   t4 = 33.75C avg  (day 36.25C / night 31.25C)  grow cycles: g12, g13, g14
!
! Varieties: BG = BG23-1251 (LU0201), WG = Waldmanns Green (LU0202)
!
! Observed final biomass at DAS35 (from biomass_complete_dataset.csv):
!   t1: BG FW=182.5g DW=7.24g,  WG FW=149.2g DW=7.09g
!   t2: BG FW=245.6g DW=11.19g, WG FW=225.7g DW=11.41g  (optimal range)
!   t3: BG FW=157.0g DW=9.80g,  WG FW=146.7g DW=9.25g
!   t4: BG FW=68.1g  DW=6.00g,  WG FW=66.5g  DW=5.70g   (heat stress)
!
! Transplant DW at DAS14 (from biomass_complete_dataset.csv, used as PLWT):
!   t1: BG=39mg WG=28mg (avg=34mg)   t2: BG=61mg WG=43mg (avg=52mg)
!   t3: BG=23mg WG=19mg (avg=21mg)   t4: BG=24mg WG=21mg (avg=23mg)
!
! Data files in /donald coon/:
!   biomass_complete_dataset.csv  - FW and DW per plant at DAS 14,21,28,35
!   transpiration_corrected.csv   - daily transpiration (mL/plant/day)
!   photos_height.csv             - canopy height (cm) from image analysis
!   photos_with_LAI.csv           - LAI from image analysis
!   fluorescence_complete.csv     - SPAD, leaf thickness, leaf temp (PhotosynQ2)
!   licor-complete-dataset.csv    - gas exchange at midday (LI-COR 6800)
!   plant_nutrition_dataset.csv   - elemental analysis of plant tissue
